src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Evening' game
01 Nov 2019, 23:58 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday evening's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Pick 3 Evening" game were:
9-7-8
(nine, seven, eight)
